  "title": "SAP BTP Architect",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a SAP BTP Data Architect to lead solution design and</p><p>delivery across SAP HANA Cloud, SAP Datasphere, and SAP Analytics</p><p>Cloud. This role combines hands-on architecture, technical leadership,</p><p>and team management.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>• Own end-to-end data and analytics architecture on SAP BTP</p><p>• Design consistent, scalable solutions across HANA Cloud, Datasphere</p><p>and SAC</p><p>• Decide optimal placement of:</p><p>• Business logic</p><p>• ETL logic</p><p>• Analytical calculations</p><p>• Define and enforce design standards and best practices</p><p>• Assign work, track delivery, and resolve technical blockers</p><p>• Act as key technical decision-maker during sprint execution</p><p>• Collaborate with Business Analysts and stakeholders on requirements</p><p>• Identify and drive future improvements (transport optimization,</p><p>versioning)</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>• Deep expertise in:<br />o SAP HANA Cloud (SQLScript, dynamic SQL, partitioning)</p><p>o SAP Datasphere modeling</p><p>o SAP Analytics Cloud reporting</p><p>• Strong solution architecture and design skills</p><p>• Proven experience leading and mentoring technical teams</p><p>• Ability to work in restricted enterprise environments (manual transpono Git)</p>",
